1. First, create a new Discord application from the Discord Developer Portal (<https://discord.com/developers/applications>). Choose a name for your bot and set the bot icon. You'll receive a bot token, which you'll need later.
2. Install Node.js (<https://nodejs.org/en/download/>) if you haven't already.
